msgctxt "an7.40:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.40:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 40. Paṭhamavasasutta → paṭhamacittavasavattanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Paṭhamavasasutta"
msgstr "40. Mastery of the Mind"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.34"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: vase → vasaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an7.40:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu cittaṃ vase vatteti, no ca "
"bhikkhu cittassa vasena vattati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities masters their mind and is not "
"mastered by it."

msgctxt "an7.40:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

# Reading kallitakusala with AN 6.24
msgctxt "an7.40:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu samādhikusalo hoti, samādhissa samāpattikusalo "
"hoti, samādhissa ṭhitikusalo hoti, samādhissa vuṭṭhānakusalo hoti, "
"samādhissa kalyāṇakusalo hoti, samādhissa gocarakusalo hoti, samādhissa "
"abhinīhārakusalo hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is skilled at immersion, skilled in entering "
"immersion, skilled in remaining in immersion, skilled in emerging from "
"immersion, skilled in gladdening the mind for immersion, skilled in the "
"mindfulness meditation subjects for immersion, and skilled in projecting the "
"mind purified by immersion."

msgctxt "an7.40:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu cittaṃ vase "
"vatteti, no ca bhikkhu cittassa vasena vattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these seven qualities masters their mind and is not "
"mastered by it.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.40:1.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
